{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c4d99c7ecf","title":"关于培养干部问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7b741fbb58","index":0,"year":1951,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"c4d99c7ecf","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949-1957卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5119d7d831","type":"title","text":"关于培养干部问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"c4d99c7ecf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8960f64a6d","type":"paragraph","text":"一、旧技术人员是国民党的遗产，是很有本领，但还不能依靠，应争取团结。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"c4d99c7ecf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d3215e85fb","type":"paragraph","text":"二、全国大中学生多是地主、资产阶级的儿女，也是国民党的遗产，但经培养改造，其中有一部分能依靠，也有一部分不能依靠。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"c4d99c7ecf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3e6e0cbf0f","type":"paragraph","text":"三、现在我们最重要的是培养技术干部的骨十，最重要的是培养我们党、军队中十多年的知识分子，还有一部分是参加土改的知识分子，可抽调天部分去训练。另一部分从工农速成中学、从工农子弟中培养一部分，即是说要这两类人经过培养后，团结上边这两种人。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"c4d99c7ecf","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":205,"end":205}},"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"595fd8cc5a","type":"paragraph","text":"2、全国大中学生多是地主、资产阶级的儿女，也是国民党的遗产，但给培养改造，其中有一部分能依靠，也有一部分不能依靠。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"c4d99c7ecf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d01e97c63","type":"paragraph","text":"关于培养干部问题，","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"c4d99c7ecf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"805925079c","type":"paragraph","text":"（钱俊瑞同志传达）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"c4d99c7ecf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"881f292db2","type":"paragraph","text":"3、现在我们最重要的是培养技术干部的骨干，最重要的是培养我们党、军队中十多年的知识分子，还有一部分是参加土改的知识分子，可抽调大部分去训练。另一部分从工农速成中学、从工农子弟中培养一部分，即是说要从这两类人经过培养后，团结上边这两种人。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"c4d99c7ecf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8b6d46c76b","type":"title","text":"关于培养干部问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"c4d99c7ecf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d02b402092","type":"paragraph","text":"1、旧技术人员是国民党的遗产，是很有本领，但还不能依靠，应争取团结。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"c4d99c7ecf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fcdfd5e5c9","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自徐方庭同志笔记本）","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"c4d99c7ecf","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":33,"end":33}}}},"__N_SSG":true}